snippet.title: Simpsons Treehouse of horror fan game Marge Simpson Patreon exclusive gameplay
snippet.description:
This is a teaser video of Patreon exclusive character Marge Simpson in my fan game The Simpsons Treehouse of horror available for PC.

UPDATE Marge is finished and available NOW for Patreons so why not support me and my game making efforts ? Patreon has loads of exclusive games, news and special content

www.patreon.com/thatcherproductions

Game made by Thatcher productions on the Openbor engine. Marge sprites by Mugen artist Warner.

www.thatcherproductions.org
